{"tid":520711,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"傳真社兩周籌百萬 夠撐4個月","createTime":"2018-01-05T16:46:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-05T17:23:27.000Z","uid":79563,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5fa783c86e48e3551910a0a9a3758fc9a6c3bb62","tid":520711,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T16:46:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20180101/s00002/1514742348325\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180101%2Fs00002%2F1514742348325&d=vVr%2FWdiuJrFGz5lifNlARcmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=0fdc8dd8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180101%2Fs00002%2F1514742348325&h=391ec75a\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20180101/s00002/1514742348325</a><br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】早前話陷入財困嘅本地獨立通訊社FactWire傳真社，經過兩星期公眾籌集資金後，籌得啱啱超過100萬元，足夠維持額外4個月嘅運作。創辦人吳曉東話，籌到嘅資金雖然同原先380萬元目標有距離，但可以暫時擺脫即時倒閉嘅危機。<br />\n<br />\n吳曉東話，最新籌集到嘅資金，由幾十蚊一筆到1萬蚊都有，亦有人選擇用年捐2555元或者月捐200元方式支持。佢仲話今次募資勢頭唔錯，相信能為傳真社爭取到額外時間。<br />\n<br />\n吳曉東認為，市民今次肯再資助傳真社，係畀緊機會、畀緊時間佢哋，佢承諾傳真社下個月會繼續發表新嘅報道，報答市民嘅支持。"},{"pid":"80a46256a5afbe5431026a7b5e0e9944a13bb00b","tid":520711,"uid":48157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T17:08:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1a554c1e84e5a19174d5d9cd8a8be231541015b1","tid":520711,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"80a46256a5afbe5431026a7b5e0e9944a13bb00b","tid":520711,"uid":48157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T17:08:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T17:23:27.000Z","msg":"連登仔好多狗衝去捐<br />\n<br />\n但人地明明係親泛民 + 反港獨<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}